Rain Mini
<img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1210869" title="I migliori zaini e borse per portatili Mac e PC" src="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/backpack-rain-mini.jpg" alt="I migliori zaini e borse per portatili Mac e PC" width="1200" height="826" srcset="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/backpack-rain-mini.jpg 1200w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/backpack-rain-mini-480x330.jpg 480w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/backpack-rain-mini-30x21.jpg 30w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/backpack-rain-mini-75x52.jpg 75w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/backpack-rain-mini-110x76.jpg 110w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/backpack-rain-mini-160x110.jpg 160w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/backpack-rain-mini-500x344.jpg 500w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/backpack-rain-mini-50x34.jpg 50w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/backpack-rain-mini-100x70.jpg 100w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/backpack-rain-mini-200x138.jpg 200w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/backpack-rain-mini-218x150.jpg 218w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/backpack-rain-mini-696x479.jpg 696w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/backpack-rain-mini-1068x735.jpg 1068w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/backpack-rain-mini-610x420.jpg 610w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" />
Alcune volte non serve uno zaino grande ma uno zaino piccolo. Il Rain mini in questo caso rappresenta la soluzione ideale. Questo zainetto minimalista presenta una tasca interna per computer portatile fino a 13″ (ottima anche per un iPad), uno spazioso scomparto principale e una tasca esterna nascosta per il telefono sul pannello posteriore e spallacci regolabili. Il Backpack Mini è realizzato in tessuto PU impermeabile  che Rains spiega essere “progettato per essere robusto, duraturo e piacevole al tatto”. È disponibile in vari colori.
